Basic tier users can access all READ (article) content but cannot watch recordings, which are typically available only to Fullstack or Elevate tier users. Recordings from add-on content types like RHEINGOLD (conference sessions), CAMP (workshops), or FLEX_CAMP (self-paced workshops) require separate purchase or add-on access regardless of the base tier.
